name: The beautiful world and its people

metadata.name: Magical Father
metadata.description: This is like a magical father we all once wanted in our life. As a that's not burned with a silver spoon on their mouth is hard for most of use to love our lives the way we wanted. We all want this unimaginable father that can provide our needs with a snap of finger. Though we can all picture him on our minds in differend ways but we all wanted that father we with magical powers that do whatever we wish for. well this is just a discription of the kind of man we all wanted as a father when we're growing up of corse life can be so hard with out this Magical Father we all wanted.
